    "These can be used as prior information, essential to build early-warning systems.",
    "Some literature can be found in this respect.",
    "For instance, a pipeline to detect GAN specific traces left during the deepfake creation is proposed in Giudice et al. (2021).",
    "The authors in the latter article employ discrete cosine transforms to detect anomalies.",
    "Moreover, an unsupervised fingerprint classification module based on anomaly detection to identify GAN images is presented in Pu et al. (2020)."
